{"id":232885520,"title":"#分享 完美的三頭肌訓練 (中文字幕)","content":"http://i.imgur.com/HnrcBxo.jpg\n\nhttp://bit.ly/35NfkWO\n\n \n這次的訓練內容介紹如何充分訓練到三頭肌，整理成一套完整的訓練內容，為了要充分訓練到三頭肌，要包含大重量的訓練動作提供足夠的刺激，同時利用遞減式訓練法加強雙槓體撐的效果，並讓三頭肌的長頭充分收縮與伸展，並在動作期間確保阻力維持在一定的力量曲線，可以利用動作模式與彈力帶輔助。\n\n完美的三頭肌訓練\n\n1.架上窄距臥推 3組 10下 6下 4下 做到力竭\n\n2.三組式負重雙槓體撐 3組做到力竭\n負重→徒手→彈力帶\n\n3A.三頭肌滑輪伸展 3組10-12RM 做到力竭\n3B.三頭肌滑式伸展 3組做到力竭 (用同樣的重量)\n\n4.搖擺三頭肌滑輪下拉 2組 12RM 做到力竭\n\n5.彈力帶仰臥三頭肌伸展 2組 15RM 做到力竭\n\n \n--\nFitting Room TW\n運動、健康相關資訊翻譯影片\n官方Blog\nhttp://fittingroomtw.blogspot.tw/\n官方臉書\nhttps://goo.gl/HZhAhS","excerpt":"這次的訓練內容介紹如何充分訓練到三頭肌，整理成一套完整的訓練內容，為了要充分訓練到三頭肌，要包含大重量的訓練動作提供足夠的刺激，同時利用遞減式訓練法加強雙槓體撐的效果，並讓三頭肌的長頭充分收縮與伸展，","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"9b5213d6-4427-4a3c-b788-efa19493631c","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-13T15:19:41.885Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-13T15:19:41.885Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":13,"tags":[],"topics":["健身","三頭肌"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"健身","forumAlias":"fitness","school":"FRTW","department":"fittingroomtw","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":13}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/HnrcBxo.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"c3e5eabb-0181-4f95-a2b0-f8f1f024d7b2","url":"https://i.imgur.com/HnrcBxol.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/HnrcBxol.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/HnrcBxol.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-13T15:19:41.885Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-13T15:19:41.885Z"},{"id":"c3e5eabb-0181-4f95-a2b0-f8f1f024d7b2","url":"http://i.imgur.com/HnrcBxo.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/HnrcBxo","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/HnrcBxol.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTAT